      "text": "Let $\\alpha,\\beta \\in \\mathbb{R}$. Is it true that\\[\\liminf_{n\\to \\infty} n \\| n\\alpha \\| \\| n\\beta\\| =0\\]where $\\|x\\|$ is the distance from $x$ to the nearest integer?"
